title: iRobot Roomba 800 Series - How To Empty Bin and Clean Filter

asset.title: iRobot Roomba 800 Series - How To Empty Bin and Clean Filter
asset.description: iRobot Roomba 800 Series - How To Empty Bin and Clean Filter
asset.author: iRobot

transcripts: To remove the bin, press the bin release button. Open the bin door to empty the bin. Close the door and return the bin to the robot. To clean the filter, remove the bin, now press and lift the filter door release tab. Remove the filter by grasping the yellow tab. Clean Roomba's filter by tapping against your trash container. To reinstall the filter, press in the middle filter lever with the side of the filter and push the filter down. The filter door will not close if the filter is not installed correctly.
